You listen to</i>

1597
02:05:44.125 --> 02:05:49.875
<i>I am the one in your life</i>

1598
02:05:50.000 --> 02:05:53.542
<i>No one can erase me</i>

1599
02:05:53.667 --> 02:05:55.708
<i>When you talk to the rest</i>

1600
02:05:55.750 --> 02:05:57.542
<i>And at times you may laugh</i>

1601
02:05:57.625 --> 02:06:01.125
<i>Deep down. you will ache</i>

1602
02:06:01.333 --> 02:06:05.708
<i>Because you're thinking of me</i>

1603
02:06:06.042 --> 02:06:08.000
I am

1604
02:06:08.083 --> 02:06:11.542
<i>The beginning and the end</i>

1605
02:06:11.625 --> 02:06:15.042
<i>Keep it well in mind that</i>

1606
02:06:15.125 --> 02:06:19.042
<i>Should you find someone else
Before too long</i>

1607
02:06:19.125 --> 02:06:22.750
<i>You will leave because</i>

1608
02:06:22.833 --> 02:06:27.500
